Investment Policy


            
            The Fund seeks capital appreciation, and a secondary goal to provide current income through dividends or interest received from its investments. The Fund invests at least 65% of its assets in equity securities of firms that mine, process, or deal in gold and other precious metals.
            
            
            

 


